data.description: Charming single level home in a great SW Boise location on quiet cul-de-sac. Cozy up next to the fireplace in the spacious living room that abounds with natural light. The open kitchen offers ample counter space and features an island cooktop/oven. The spacious master bedroom includes a bay window, double closets, & en-suite bathroom w/jetted tub & separate walk-in shower. The private fenced backyard is perfect for entertaining & is plumbed for your gas BBQ. Community Park with walking paths and playground. This home is close to shopping and many amenities, & is just minutes from The Village at Meridian, Town Center Mall, Boise Airport & freeway access. Brand new carpet, new HVAC in 2021, water heater 2017 & plumbed for central vac.
